snippet.textDisplay:
Are you still going to record them during the tour this year?
This video alone made me realize that it's not all about recording and saving the performance. You should look at them as people, with your actual eyes and burn the image so you will never forget. You DON'T need to record. You remember experiences better through your true eyes rather than a camera's imo. I recorded a lot of the concert I went to and I regret it... It was distracting. I could have looked at them directly but I was too focused on my phone's camera to remember much... They weren't even good shots. It's not worth it 😔
